column5: Hi all,  I am just wondering if there is a season regulation on Petro-Canada Park?  it is close to my house and i would like to fish there all year round  Thanks
Closes Jan 1st the Parking is closed but u can still go down and fish
I think the seasons last day is the 31st of Dec... you can fish year round south of hwy 2 though... Its in the regs
